parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected cracking or shattering of the windshield can cause a loss of visibility, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Windshield cracks or shatters without any visible impact or damage
cracks spread rapidly
cracks appear in the center of the windshield
cracks originate from the bottom of the windshield
windshield shatters into a spider web pattern.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiper blade can cause reduced visibility during rain or snow, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Wiper blade detaches from the vehicle
wiper blade fails to clear water or snow from the windshield

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
often when the driver is attempting to brake or slow down. The brakes may fail to engage
or the vehicle may lunge forward unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunction of the adaptive cruise control system can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.

displays "no preceding vehicle
" and disengages
causing the vehicle to accelerate or fail to brake in response to changing traffic conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the radar-assisted cruise control system can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The system fails to detect preceding vehicles or road conditions
causing the vehicle to accelerate or fail to brake in response to changing traffic conditions.
